Federal Reserve Bank of Atlanta 
President Dennis Lockhart moderates a panel on the  U.S. economy  
in Atlanta.  David M. Walker, a former U.S. comptroller general, and 
William H. Rogers Jr., president and chief executive officer of 
SunTrust Banks Inc., also speak. Lockhart said the U.S. is 
starting to recognize the significance of finding a solution to 
its fiscal woes. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 01:00:21
 